{
  "texts": [
    "Examples of this already exist, such as Lux Aeterna who produced a sci-fi movie, RENO, as part of the MyWorld Strength in Places Programme, as a means of exploring AI tool-sets in visual effects, Hifle (2024).",
    "This RENO production was used to explore the use of AI in post-production, however such work could be elevated to production-oriented tasks.",
    "Alternatively, we can envision using 3-D reconstructions of real scenes, discussed in Sect. 3.2, to achieve more reliable tests on real scenarios.",
    "This would provide more relatable results for cinematographers that intend using IC to direct cameras in real environments, as well as those that wish capture cinematic footage using 3-D reconstructions.",
    "With respect to supporting the cinematographic language, there are many considerations."
  ]
}